隐私政策

欢迎使用订单生成器App！本隐私政策旨在向您解释我们如何收集、使用、存储和保护您的个人信息。请在使用本应用之前仔细阅读本隐私政策。

1. 信息收集与使用：
   - 设备信息：我们可能会收集您的设备信息，包括设备型号、操作系统版本等，用于应用的优化和改进。
   - 使用数据：我们会收集有关您使用定时煮蛋器应用的数据，例如设置的计时器时间、使用频率等，以便改进应用性能。

2. 个人信息保护：
   - 数据安全：我们采取合理的安全措施来保护您的个人信息免受未经授权的访问、披露或损害。
   - 数据存储：您的个人信息将可能存储在我们的服务器上，我们将尽力保障数据的安全性。

3. 信息共享与披露：
   - 我们不会与第三方共享您的个人信息，除非获得您的明确同意或法律要求。
   - 我们可能会使用第三方服务提供商来支持应用的功能，但他们仅在必要情况下才能访问您的信息。

4. 隐私选择：
   - 您可以选择不提供某些信息，但这可能会影响应用的某些功能。
   - 您可以随时通过应用设置或联系我们来更新或删除您的个人信息。

5. 儿童隐私：我们的应用不面向13岁以下的儿童。如果您是父母或监护人，不应允许您的孩子提交个人信息。

6. 隐私政策变更：
   - 我们可能会不时更新本隐私政策，更新后的政策将在应用内公布。您继续使用应用即表示您同意新的隐私政策。

7. 联系我们：如果您对隐私政策有任何疑问或意见，请向我们发送电子邮件至 hjl20230816@163.com。

日期：2023年09月15日

Privacy Policy

Welcome to the Order Generator App! This privacy policy is designed to explain to you how we collect, use, store and protect your personal information. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using this App.

1. Information collection and use:
    - Device information: We may collect your device information, including device model, operating system version, etc., for application optimization and improvement.
    - Usage data: We will collect data about your use of the Timer Egg Boiler app, such as set timer time, frequency of use, etc., in order to improve app performance.

2. Personal information protection:
    - Data Security: We take reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure or damage.
    - Data storage: Your personal information will likely be stored on our servers, and we will do our best to ensure the security of the data.

3. Information Sharing and Disclosure:
    - We will not share your personal information with third parties unless we obtain your explicit consent or are required by law.
    - We may use third-party service providers to support the functionality of the App, but they will only have access to your information when necessary.

4. Privacy Choices:
    - You can choose not to provide certain information, but this may affect some functionality of the app.
    - You can update or delete your personal information at any time through the application settings or contact us.

5. Children's Privacy: Our applications are not intended for children under 13 years of age. If you are a parent or guardian, you should not allow your children to submit personal information.

6. Privacy Policy Changes:
    - We may update this privacy policy from time to time, and the updated policy will be published within the app. Your continued use of the App constitutes your agreement to the new Privacy Policy.

7. Contact us: If you have any questions or comments about the Privacy Policy, please send us an email at hjl20230816@163.com.

Date: September 15, 2023
